{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "GA juhsu Deewa Pahrmahzi-\nfchannu/ winna Angstibu/ winna\nspehzigu Rohlu/ un winna is-\nsteepnu Effkonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Sihnes/ un\nwinna Darbus/ ko wiꞥſch Egip-\ntes Widdi darrija pee Warais\nto Egiptes Rehnitu/ un pee wiſ-\nfas winna Semnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ko wiꞥſch darrijs irr\npee to Egiptezu Karra-Spehka/\npee winna Sirgeem/ un pee wiſ-\nna Ratteem / ka wiꞥſch likke to\nUhdeni Needras-Juhra pahr win-\nneem fagahstees / kad tee jums\npakkatdsinnahs / un tas KUNG̅\nnomaitaja tohs lihds tchoddeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ko wiꞥſch jums darrijs\nirr Tukfnezji/ teekams juhs us fcho\nWeetu efat nahkucht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ko wiꞥſch darrijs irr\nDatanam un Abiramam Celia-\nba/ Ruhbera Dehla/ Dehleem/\nka ta Semme sawu Mutti at-\ndarrija/ un aprithje tohs ar win-\nnu Gainehm / un ar winnu\nDshwofteem/ un ar winno Pa-\ndohmu/ kaﬆterem peederreja/ wiſ-\nfa Israëka Widdii.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo juhsfas Azzis irr redsej-\nchas wiſsu fcho leelu Darbu ta\nKUNGA/ ko wiꞥſch darrijs irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nu turrajt wiſsus tohs\nBanslus/ ko es tchoddeen tew pa-\nwehtu/ ka juhs stiprinati tohpat/\nun nahkat / un eemantojat to\nSemmi/ us kurren juhs eetat /\nwinnu eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka juhs ilgi dshwojat wirs\ntahs Semmes / fo tas KUNG̅\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "juhsfeem Tehweem swebrejs/win-\nneem un winna Dsimnumam\ndoht/weenu Semmi/ kas ar Pee-\nnu un Meddu tekk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta Semme / us kur-\nren tu fraiga to eemantoht/ ne ir-\nka Egiptes-Semme/ no kurrenes\njuhs efat isgahjuſchi / ko tu ap-\nfehji ar tauwu Sehktu/ un to pats\naplaisitiit/ itt ka weenu Rahpoh-\nsto-Dahrsu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ta Semme / us kur-\nren juhs eetat winnu eemantoht/\nirr weena Semme ar Kalneem\nun Eelejahm/wizza tohp flazzita\nar Uhdeni no Debbes Leetus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weena Semme/ ko tas\nKUNG̅S taws Deeus apgah-\nda/ us ko ta KUNGA taiwa Dee-\nta Azzis bes Mittefchanas stat-\ntahs/ no Gadda Gefahkuma lihds\nGadda Gallain.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja juhs labbi klausifeet\nmanneem Bautleem/ ko es jums\nschodeen pawehſtu/ un mihlefeit to\nKUNG̅U juhsfu Deewu/ un win-\nnam kalpofeit no wiſnas juhsas\nSirđs / un no wiſnas juhsas\nDivehſeles.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dohschu es Leetu juh-\nfu Semmē sawā Laika/ agri un\nwehlu/ ka tu tawn Labbibu / un\ntawn Wihnu/ un tawn Etji war-\nrt sakraht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es dohschu Sahli tai-\nwā Lankā preekch taiweem Loh-\npeim/ un tu ehdiſt un pee-ehdiſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sargajeetes / ka juhsu\nSirđs ne tohp pahrrunnata / ka\njuhs atkahpjat/ un kalpojat zit-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
